meaningMnemonic: Remember 主観的 meaning "subjective"? This is the counterpart to that. And since <kanji>guest</kanji>s' and customers' <kanji>view</kanji>s are always objectively right, this means <vocabulary>objective</vocabulary>.
readingMnemonic: This is a jukugo word, which usually means on'yomi readings from the kanji. If you know the readings of your kanji you'll know how to read this as well.
